_:c8dd9381bfa0e2597e8f3cb79fd57156 a <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E52_Time-span> ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> " He was a medieval holy saint, a disciple of  \n                  \n                     ʾabbāTakla Hāymānot, who lived during the reigns \n                  of Wǝdǝm Raʿad, ʿAmda Ṣǝyon I and\n                  Sayfa ʾArʿad. He is credited with the foundation of the monastery of  \n                  Dabra Bankʷal, near ʾAksum during the reign of King \n                  Sayfa ʾArʿad. It is also reported that King Sayfa ʾArʿad visited him and\n                  richly endowned the monastery Dabra Bankʷal with lands in Tǝgray\n               " .
